You are implementing `lib/deterministic-pipeline.ts`, a deterministic rendering pipeline for the PDD video editor. When `PDD_DETERMINISTIC_PIPELINE=1`, this module generates predictable, repeatable assets (specs, components, TTS scripts, Veo clips) so the pipeline can verify timing, audio sync, and final stitching without relying on AI-generated content.

